name: Yesterday's object access compared to mean
description: A chart showing yesterday's access for monitored SQL objects (bars) and comparing those values to their historical means (red ticks). The bars are also colored according to the z-score for yesterday's access.

title.text: Number of SQL detected yesterday compared to the object's historical average
title.subtitle: Historical averages shown as red ticks. Only z-scores above 1 or below -1 shown

transform.calculate: (datum['$primary_measure'] - datum['Average execution per day']) / datum['Std. deviation']
